# üïµÔ∏è‚Äç‚ôÇÔ∏è OSINT Flask Scanner

A simple web application for automated OSINT data collection from a given domain. Results include WHOIS info, DNS records, IP data, SSL certificates, and subdomains (via crt.sh). Also generates a downloadable PDF report.

## Features
- Domain-based scanning
- Subdomain enumeration (crt.sh)
- IP geolocation & SSL cert info
- WHOIS and DNS info
- Auto-generated PDF report
- Flask-based web interface

## Run Locally

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/osint-flask-scanner.git
cd osint-flask-scanner
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py
